# Button — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/button.css`

## Architecture

ALL visual styling lives in the CSS file. React components compose CSS class names only via `clsx` — no Tailwind utilities in React.

- **`@apply`**: layout, alignment, spacing, sizing, typography, radius, colors, basic shadows, cursor, select, whitespace, position
- **Raw CSS**: multi-property `transition`, `@keyframes`, `[data-theme]` overrides, `@media (hover:hover)` hover blocks, `::before`/`::after` pseudo-elements, compound `box-shadow` stacks, `backdrop-filter`

## CSS Classes

### Base

```css
.acko-btn {
  @apply inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-medium
         leading-none border-none cursor-pointer select-none
         whitespace-nowrap no-underline relative;
  font-family: inherit;
  transition: background-color 150ms ease, color 150ms ease,
              border-color 150ms ease, transform 100ms ease,
              box-shadow 150ms ease;
}
```

### Sizes (via `@apply` for height, padding, font, radius)

| Class | Implementation |
|-------|---------------|
| `.acko-btn-xs` | `@apply h-8 px-4 text-xs rounded-full; line-height: 16px;` |
| `.acko-btn-sm` | `@apply h-10 px-4 text-sm rounded-full; line-height: 18px;` |
| `.acko-btn-md` | `@apply h-12 px-4 text-base leading-6 rounded-full;` |
| `.acko-btn-lg` | `@apply h-14 px-6 text-lg rounded-full; line-height: 28px;` |
| `.acko-btn-xl` | `@apply h-16 px-8 text-xl rounded-full; line-height: 32px;` |

### Variants (via `@apply` for colors + raw CSS for complex shadows)

| Class | Background | Text | Shadow |
|-------|-----------|------|--------|
| `.acko-btn-primary` | `bg-primary` | `text-on-primary` | `shadow-btn-inner` |
| `.acko-btn-secondary` | `bg-btn-secondary-bg` | `text-primary` | `shadow-btn-inner` |
| `.acko-btn-outline` | `bg-transparent` | `text-btn-outline-color` | `inset 0 0 0 1px var(--color-btn-outline-color)` |
| `.acko-btn-ghost` | `bg-transparent` | `text-btn-ghost-color` | none |
| `.acko-btn-danger` | `bg-transparent` | `text-error` | `inset 0 0 0 1px var(--color-error)` |

### Icon Sizing (inside CSS via `@apply`)

```css
.acko-btn-icon { @apply inline-flex items-center justify-center shrink-0; }
.acko-btn-xs .acko-btn-icon { @apply size-3; }
.acko-btn-sm .acko-btn-icon { @apply size-3.5; }
.acko-btn-md .acko-btn-icon { @apply size-4; }
.acko-btn-lg .acko-btn-icon { @apply size-[18px]; }
.acko-btn-xl .acko-btn-icon { @apply size-5; }
```

### Icon-Only (square button via `@apply`)

```css
.acko-btn-icon-only.acko-btn-xs { @apply w-8 p-0; }
.acko-btn-icon-only.acko-btn-sm { @apply w-10 p-0; }
.acko-btn-icon-only.acko-btn-md { @apply w-12 p-0; }
.acko-btn-icon-only.acko-btn-lg { @apply w-14 p-0; }
.acko-btn-icon-only.acko-btn-xl { @apply w-16 p-0; }
```

### Full Width

```css
.acko-btn-full-width { @apply w-full; }
```

### States

#### Loading
```css
.acko-btn-loading { @apply pointer-events-none; color: transparent !important; }
```

#### Disabled
```css
.acko-btn-disabled,
.acko-btn:disabled {
  @apply cursor-not-allowed opacity-100;
  background-color: var(--color-disabled-bg) !important;
  color: var(--color-disabled-text) !important;
  box-shadow: none !important;
}
```

### Spinner (raw CSS — animation)

```css
.acko-btn-spinner {
  @apply absolute size-[18px] rounded-full;
  border: 2px solid currentColor;
  border-right-color: transparent;
  animation: acko-spin 600ms linear infinite;
}
```

Spinner colors per variant via raw CSS:
| Variant | Spinner `color` |
|---------|----------------|
| primary | `--color-on-primary` |
| secondary | `--color-text-default` |
| outline | `--color-text-default` |
| ghost | `--color-btn-ghost-color` |
| danger | `--color-error` |

## Hover States (raw CSS — `@media (hover: hover)`)

Wrapped in `@media (hover: hover) and (pointer: fine)`:

| Variant | Hover treatment |
|---------|----------------|
| primary | dark overlay gradient + compound `box-shadow` (inner + hover) |
| secondary | `bg-surface-raised-hover` + `shadow-btn-secondary-hover` |
| outline | `bg-btn-outline-hover-bg` + compound inset + hover shadow |
| ghost | `bg-btn-ghost-hover-bg` |
| danger | `bg-error-subtle` + compound inset + error glow shadow |

## Active State (raw CSS)

`:active:not(:disabled)` → `transform: scale(0.97)`.

## Focus State (raw CSS)

`:focus-visible` → `outline: none; box-shadow: var(--shadow-focus-ring)`.
Outline variant adds compound shadow: inset border + focus ring.

## Dark Theme Overrides (raw CSS)

Scoped under `[data-theme="dark"]`:
- secondary: text changes to `text-default` (via `--color-text-default`)
- primary hover: uses `--color-btn-primary-hover-bg`, no gradient overlay
- secondary hover: lighter inner shadow `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)`
- shadows switch automatically via semantic token remapping in `tokens.css`

## Elevated Theme Overrides (raw CSS)

Scoped under `[data-theme="elevated"]`:

### Primary
- `background: var(--elevated-primary-gradient)` + `box-shadow: var(--elevated-primary-shadow)`
- `::before` pseudo for convex overlay
- Hover: `translateY(-1px)` lift + intensified gradient/shadow

### Secondary
- Glass background via `backdrop-filter: blur(14px)`

### Outline
- Border gradient via `background: padding-box + border-box` technique

### Ghost
- Uses `--color-primary-active` for text

### Focus
- `--elevated-focus-ring` (includes glass border stroke)

## Transitions (raw CSS)

```css
transition: background-color 150ms ease,
            color 150ms ease,
            border-color 150ms ease,
            transform 100ms ease,
            box-shadow 150ms ease;
```

## Keyframes (raw CSS)

```css
@keyframes acko-spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
```
